{"tid":1749850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Trump想睇埋區選再決定簽唔簽人權法","createTime":"2019-11-24T07:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T00:18:39.000Z","uid":105018,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81f5c2e0bfaca28a6dd8da3956df7eff26184612","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"本身諗緊trump唔簽住係咪凈係因為trade deal<br />\n今日睇到呢篇新聞<br />\n突然connect到 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Trump係想睇區選反應點再決定簽唔簽呀！</span></span><br />\n如果區選班垃圾賣港大敗 trump就可以有更加強既理由去簽<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">相反 如果仲係賣港派贏 美國要pass個bill個理據就會弱好撚多</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以快撚啲去投票唔該！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191124&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60302819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191124%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60302819&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=b75eabfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191124%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60302819&h=0cd7946f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191124&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60302819</a><br />\n<br />\n新增動新聞】美國白宮國家安全顧問奧布萊恩（Robert O'Brien）周六表示，中美仍有可能在本年內簽署首階段貿易協議，但同時表示總統特朗普不會對香港發生的事視而不見。他表示，美國希望香港區議會選舉在沒有暴力事件的情況下舉行，認為那會是「好兆頭」。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩在加拿大哈利法克斯出席國際安全論壇期間對記者說：「我們希望最遲本年底達成（首階段）協議&hellip;&hellip;同時，但我們不會對香港、南中國海以至世界其他地區發生的事情視而不見。」<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩表示，美國不希望六四天安門鎮壓在香港重演，「我們已經在香港看到太多暴力事件了&hellip;&hellip;真正問題是一旦中國鐵腕鎮壓示威，世界會如何回應？美國一定會盡其本份」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會日前通過《香港人權與民主法案》，正待特朗普簽署生效。特朗普周五未有回應會否簽署法案，只稱「我們要跟香港並肩，但我也跟（中國國家主席）習近平並肩」，又說其政府會仔細檢視法案內容。"},{"pid":"d9c99154fbe8ec1dac9aba4c81f4400c3893b974","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a2bdd46261062e3ed610d33a1ffc156aa9dc4adf","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"快撚啲投"},{"pid":"c63bf2e2bbead697e23b5d65a8eb01102cc46acf","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"唔投既話會造成一連串影響"},{"pid":"ff637322792444de2f4c5f87a6ddaa4193677f35","tid":1749850,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc44d7ca785ca3817e34b743fe3eb130c01515ca","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"84b2ac61c34ef383f638448e673f5b602536fc25","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff637322792444de2f4c5f87a6ddaa4193677f35","tid":1749850,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣請入</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f889cbe4a626ba87bc2e7b12bb8ca62de3629fb","tid":1749850,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684c0e51b70cbffc6c5b79e7573ba97315d6a7f5","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"快啲投"},{"pid":"cb1bc41ef24d57d1e4854324fb8d3a548b14a47f","tid":1749850,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"咪比賣港派贏"},{"pid":"acd615729992ee33e8e6c843bf422666170037b7","tid":1749850,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T0